    <NoteCard 
        key={note._id} 
        note={note} 
        onNoteUpdated={fetchNotes}
        onNoteDeleted={fetchNotes}  // Same callback to refresh list
    />
))}
```

## Key Points
- `e.preventDefault()` and `e.stopPropagation()` prevent Link navigation when clicking delete
- `window.confirm()` shows a browser confirmation dialog before deleting
- Uses DELETE method with the note ID
- Shows toast notifications for success/error feedback
- `isDeleting` state disables button during deletion to prevent double-clicks
- Callback refreshes the notes list after successful deletion

