# Custom Delete Popup Implementation (Replace Browser Confirm)

## Goal
Replace native `window.confirm()` with a reusable, custom-designed delete confirmation modal.

## 1. Create Reusable Modal (`src/components/ConfirmDeleteModal.jsx`)

```jsx
import { AlertTriangle, X } from 'lucide-react';

const ConfirmDeleteModal = ({
    isOpen,
    onClose,
    onConfirm,
    isDeleting = false,
    title = 'Delete note?',
    message = 'This action cannot be undone. This note will be permanently removed.'
